description: Polling stations close after four days of voting in the island-wide election.
title: Guernsey Election 2020: Polls close in island-wide election
title_page: Guernsey Election 2020: Polls close in island-wide election - BBC News
maintext: The 38 candidates that receive the most votes will be elected to the States of Guernsey with their term due to last from 16 October until the next election in June 2025.
